====Usage notes====
{{lang|zh|覆}} was always simplified to {{zh-l|复|tr=-}} in 1964-1986, but now it still simplifies to {{zh-l|复|tr=-}} only in the meaning of "to return/reply". So words like {{zh-l|*答覆}}, {{zh-l|*反覆}} and {{zh-l|*回覆}} still simplify to {{zh-l|答复|tr=-}}, {{zh-l|反复|tr=-}} and {{zh-l|回复|tr=-}} in Simplified Chinese respectively. But in other meanings, {{lang|zh|覆}} no longer simplifies to {{zh-l|*复}}, e.g. {{zh-l|*翻覆}}, {{zh-l|*覆蓋}}, {{zh-l|*顛覆}}, {{zh-l|*傾覆}}, {{zh-l|*覆轍}}.

